text: The Philippine Star is a daily broadsheet newspaper in the Philippines. It was established on July 28, 1986 and is owned and published by PhilSTAR Daily, Inc. by veteran journalists Max Soliven, Betty Go-Belmonte and Art Borjal in the wake of the EDSA People Power Revolution. ==Other websites== * Category:1986 establishments in the Philippines Category:National newspapers published in the Philippines
title: The Philippine Star
